温和的海洋使波特兰的夜间温度高于0度，因而冬天结[[霜|霜]]很罕见。波特兰岛每年平均只会出现8次结霜，远低于英国的平均每年55.6天结霜。<ref name="UKaverages" /><ref name="wandptemperature">{{cite web | year = 2005 | language = en | url = http://www.geoffkirby.co.uk/Weather/Temperature/ | title = Temperature and Frost | publisher = Geoff Kirby | accessdate = 2006-11-18 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20081201110811/http://www.geoffkirby.co.uk/Weather/Temperature | archive-date = 2008-12-01 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>[[雪|雪]]天在这里同样罕见，每年最多只有6天在下雪，<ref name="metofficesnow">{{cite web|year=2001 |language=en |url=http://www.metoffice.gov.uk/climate/uk/averages/19712000/dl/17.gif |title=Met Office UK snow lying days |publisher=Met Office |accessdate=2006-10-18 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070809125155/http://www.metoffice.gov.uk/climate/uk/averages/19712000/dl/17.gif |archivedate=2007-08-09 }}</ref> 通常，整个冬天只会有一天下点零星小雪，雪花还没落地就会融化<ref name="annualweather2" />。在西南英格兰沿海，波特兰的冬天是最暖和的。<ref name="metofficewinter">{{cite web|year=2001 |language=en |url=http://www.metoffice.gov.uk/climate/uk/averages/19712000/tmean/16.gif |title=Met Office UK winter climate |publisher=Met Office |accessdate=2006-11-12 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100531061625/http://www.metoffice.gov.uk/climate/uk/averages/19712000/tmean/16.gif |archivedate=2010-05-31 }}</ref> 波特兰较少受到[[大西洋|大西洋]]飓风的影响，当地植物的生长季节长达9-12个月。<ref name="hardinesszones">{{cite web | year = 1999 | language = en | url = http://www.gardenweb.com/zones/europe/ | title = Hardiness Zone Map for Europe | publisher = GardenWeb | accessdate = 2007-06-20 | archive-date = 2007-06-29 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20070629194559/http://www.gardenweb.com/zones/europe/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>{{ref label|growingseason|D|D}}

[[File:Weymouth_Climatic_Graph.PNG|right]]
韦茅斯-波特兰以及南部海岸的其他城市<ref name="metofficeengland">{{cite web|year=2005 |language=en |url=http://www.metoffice.gov.uk/climate/uk/location/england/index.html |title=Met Office: English climate |publisher=Met Office |accessdate=2006-11-06 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070525051524/http://www.metoffice.gov.uk/climate/uk/location/england/index.html |archivedate=2007-05-25 }}</ref> 享有英国最充足的阳光。<ref name="jurassiccoast" /><ref name="sunshine">{{cite web | year = 2007 | language = en | url = http://property.timesonline.co.uk/tol/life_and_style/property/buying_and_selling/article2875491.ece | title = Bring me sunshine | publisher = Times Online | accessdate = 2008-03-08 | archive-date = 2008-05-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20080512085002/http://property.timesonline.co.uk/tol/life_and_style/property/buying_and_selling/article2875491.ece | dead-url = no }}</ref> 在1971年到2000年间，这里每年平均有1768.4小时的日照时间，<ref name="annualweather2" /> 超出理论可能的40%，较英国平均水平1339.7小时高出32%。<ref name="UKaverages">{{cite web|year=2001 |language=en |url=http://www.metoffice.gov.uk/climate/uk/averages/19712000/areal/uk.html |title=UK 1971-2000 averages |publisher=Met Office |accessdate=2007-08-04 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090705140124/http://www.metoffice.gov.uk/climate/uk/averages/19712000/areal/uk.html |archivedate=2009-07-05 }}</ref> 过去9年中的4年，年日照时间更是超过2000小时。<ref name="annualweather2" /> 12月是一年之中云系最多和[[湿度|湿度]]最高的月份（平均55.7小时日照，90.9毫米降雨）；相反，6月是一年之中光照最多，湿度最低的月份（平均235.1小时日照，35.6毫米降水）。<ref name="annualweather2" /> 波特兰的年降雨量低于英国平均水平，尤其在于夏季，这里的年降雨量为751.7毫米，远低于英国的平均值1125毫米。<ref name="UKaverages" />

