== 教育 ==
切希尔教育合作公司在南多塞特有5所[[幼儿学校|幼儿学校]]，4所[[初级学校|初级学校]]，12所[[小学|小学]]，4所[[高级中学|高级中学]]和2所[[特殊学校|特殊学校]]。<ref name="dorsetforyou" /> 69.8%的波特兰居民拥有学历，这稍稍低于多塞特郡的平均水平73.8%。<ref name="dorsetforyou" /> 10.2%的当地居民拥有更高的学历（Further education Lv.4+），这同样少于多塞特郡的平均水平18.3%。<ref name="dorsetforyou" />

在波特兰岛上，有两所幼儿学校，分别是福顿斯维尔的布拉肯伯里幼儿学校（Portland—Brackenbury Infant School）和格鲁夫的格鲁夫幼儿学校（Grove Infant School）；两所初级学校：福顿斯维尔的昂德希尔社区初级学校（Underhill Community Junior School）和多普希尔初级学校（Tophill Junior School）；两所小学：在韦斯顿的圣乔治小学（St George's Primary School）和在索斯维尔的索斯维尔小学（Southwell Primary School）。<ref name="dorsetla">{{cite web | year = 2007 | language = en | url = http://www1.dorsetforyou.com/Learning/SIS.nsf/ByCategory?OpenForm&Count=1000&cat=Pyramids&id=Chesil%20Education%20Partnership | title = LA Schools | publisher = Dorset County Council | accessdate = 2008-01-04 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110710144716/http://www1.dorsetforyou.com/Learning/SIS.nsf/ByCategory?OpenForm&Count=1000&cat=Pyramids&id=Chesil%20Education%20Partnership | archivedate = 2011-07-10 }}</ref> 在韦斯顿的皇家庄园艺术学院（Royal Manor Arts College）是波特兰唯一的一所高级中学，然而，这里并没有[[预科|预科]]学院。在2007年，57%的皇家庄园艺术学院学生以A*-C的成绩获得5门或5门以上的[[普通中等教育证书|普通中等教育证书]]（GCSE）。<ref name="rmac">{{cite web | year = 2007 | language = en | url = http://www.dorsetecho.co.uk/news/local/display.var.1954728.0.school_report_of_mixed_fortunes.php | title = School report of mixed fortunes | publisher = Dorset Echo | accessdate = 2008-01-10 | archive-date = 2008-07-05 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20080705150606/http://www.dorsetecho.co.uk/news/local/display.var.1954728.0.school_report_of_mixed_fortunes.php | dead-url = no }}</ref>

一些学生前往韦茅斯进修[[英国普通教育高级程度证书|大英普通教育高级程度证书]]（A-Levels）或进入其他三所切希尔教育合作公司的高中就读。齐克雷尔的预科学院巴德茅斯学院（Budmouth College）在2006年一共拥有296名学生。<ref name="sixthform">{{cite web|year=2006 |language=en |url=http://localinfo.dorsetecho.co.uk/li/secondary_schools_a_level.in.Weymouth |title=Secondary Schools (A-Level) in Weymouth |publisher=Dorset Echo |accessdate=2008-01-04 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071030134924/http://localinfo.dorsetecho.co.uk/li/secondary_schools_a_level.in.Weymouth |archivedate=2007-10-30 }}</ref> 梅坎贝里杰斯的韦茅斯学院（Weymouth College）是一家[[高等教育|高等教育]]学院，拥有大约7,500个学生，他们来自[[西南英格兰|西南英格兰]]或海外，<ref name="weymouthcollege">{{cite web|year=2007 |language=en |url=http://www.weymouth.ac.uk/the-college/welcome.html |title=About Us |publisher=Weymouth College |accessdate=2008-01-04 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080530161535/http://www.weymouth.ac.uk/the-college/welcome.html |archivedate=2008-05-30 }}</ref> 大约1,500名学生在攻读[[普通教育高级程度证书|普通教育高级程度证书]]（A-Level）的课程。<ref name="sixthform" /> 在2006年英国高等院校招生办公室给予的[[评分|评分]]（UCAS points）中，巴德茅斯学院的学生平均分为647.6，韦茅斯学院的学生则获得614.1分。<ref name="sixthform" /> 一些攻读高中学历和普通教育高级程度证书（A-Level）的学生前往多塞特郡进入托马斯·哈德耶学校（The Thomas Hardye School）继续进修。在2007年，79%的哈德耶学生收到了5门或5门以上成绩从A*-C的中等教育普通证书，78%的学生以A-C的成绩获得[[普通教育高级程度证书|普通教育高级程度证书]]（A-Level）。<ref name="thomashardye">{{cite web|year=2007 |language=en |url=http://www.thomas-hardye.dorset.sch.uk/info/results-2007.htm |title=Results – The Thomas Hardye School |publisher=The Thomas Hardye School |accessdate=2008-01-04 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080411041353/http://www.thomas-hardye.dorset.sch.uk/info/results-2007.htm |archivedate=2008-04-11 }}</ref>{{ref label|education|B|B}}

== 文化 ==
=== 体育和娱乐 ===
[[File:2006nationals2.jpg|thumb]]
在2000年，韦茅斯-波特兰国立帆船运动中心（Weymouth and Portland National Sailing Academy）在鱼鹰港建立。韦茅斯海湾被[[英国皇家帆船协会|英国皇家帆船协会]]（Royal Yachting Association）认为是全欧洲北部最好的港湾。<ref name="wpnsa">{{cite web|year=2005 |language=en |url=http://www.weymouth.gov.uk/London2012/home.asp?svid=14 |title=2012 Olympic Games sailing venue |publisher=Weymouth and Portland Borough Council |accessdate=2006-11-12 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20061231110947/http://www.weymouth.gov.uk/London2012/home.asp?svid=14 |archivedate=2006-12-31 }}</ref> 韦茅斯-波特兰定期在韦茅斯海湾举办地方性，全国性或国际性的帆船比赛，其中包括2005年的J/24世锦赛，2004年[[2004年夏季奥林匹克运动会|雅典奥运会]]选拔赛，2006年[[ISAF|ISAF]]（世界帆船总会）世锦赛以及皇家帆船协会国内青年锦标赛。<ref name="wpnsaevents">{{cite web|year=2006 |language=en |url=http://www.wpnsa.org.uk/pressreleases.htm |title=WPNSA - press releases |publisher=Weymouth and Portland National Sailing Academy |accessdate=2006-11-12 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20061202013033/http://www.wpnsa.org.uk/pressreleases.htm |archivedate=2006-12-02 }}</ref>

韦茅斯海湾和波特兰港也举办其他水上体育赛事比如[[风筝冲浪|风筝冲浪]]和[[帆板|帆板]]。切希尔海滩和波特兰港是人们垂钓，潜水，划船和游泳的场所。<ref name="watersports">{{cite web|year=2006 |language=en |url=http://www.weymouth.gov.uk/Leisure/Watersports/home.asp?svid=69 |title=Watersports in Weymouth and Portland |publisher=Weymouth and Portland Borough Council |accessdate=2006-11-12 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20061010232523/http://www.weymouth.gov.uk/Leisure/Watersports/home.asp?svid=69 |archivedate=2006-10-10 }}</ref> 当地的石灰岩悬崖和采石场被用于[[攀岩|攀岩]]，波特兰还有有供人[[抱石|抱石]]和[[深水攀岩|深水攀岩]]的场所，但是，有保护的[[攀石|攀石]]在当地才最受欢迎。<ref name="rock climbing">{{cite web | year = 2007 | language = en | url = http://www.rockfax.com/databases/results_area.html?id=5 | title = World Rock Climbing Information: Portland | publisher = Rockfax | accessdate = 2007-05-19 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20070928110119/http://www.rockfax.com/databases/results_area.html?id=5 | archive-date = 2007-09-28 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>
自从2003年6月起，波特兰岛沿岸的21.3千米成为了西南海岸步道（South West Coast Path National Trail）的一部分。<ref>{{cite book|last=South West Coast Path Association| language = en ||authorlink=:en:South West Coast Path Association|title=South West Coast Path 2009 Guide|publisher=SWCPA|date=2009|pages=94|isbn=978-0-907055-15-0}}</ref>

=== 兔子 ===
[[File:PortlandQuarry.jpg|thumb]]
[[兔子|兔子]]长期被波特兰居民视为厄运的象征，在当地非常忌讳兔子（Rabbit）这个单词的，兔子一般被称作地下老来俏（Underground Mutton），长耳多毛怪（Long-Eared Furry Things）或兔崽子（bunnies）。<ref name="wallaceandgromit">{{cite web | year = 2006 | language = en | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/england/dorset/4318710.stm | title = Wallace and Gromit spook island | publisher = [[British_Broadcasting_Corporation|British Broadcasting Corporation]] | accessdate = 2007-07-26 | archive-date = 2009-04-13 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20090413193908/http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/england/dorset/4318710.stm | dead-url = no }}</ref> 对兔子的恐惧最早来自采石场的工人，当他们看到兔子出现在洞穴中，立刻会有石头掉落，这经常造成矿工的受伤甚至死亡。<ref name="rabbits" /> 如果工人们看到了兔子，他们会立刻收拾工具回到家中，直到确认安全后才会重返工作岗位。<ref name="wallaceandgromit" />

甚至到了今天，一些年长的波特兰居民听到有人提及兔子时仍会受到冒犯或者默不作声，<ref name="rabbits">{{cite web|year=2006 |language=en |url=http://www.weymouth.gov.uk/main.asp?svid=784 |title=Rabbits, the Portland taboo word |publisher=Weymouth and Portland Borough Council |accessdate=2007-07-26 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071024070726/http://www.weymouth.gov.uk/main.asp?svid=784 |archivedate=2007-10-24 }}</ref> 在2005年10月，电影公司在当地宣传[[酷狗寶貝之魔兔詛咒|酷狗寶貝之魔兔詛咒]]时，还特地更改了电影的标题，以''Something bunny is going on''作为取代。<ref name="wallaceandgromit" />

=== 文学 ===
伯纳德·康威尔在他的历史小说《君王编年史》（{{lang|en|''The Warlord Chronicles''}}）中将波特兰岛称为死岛（Isle of the Dead），一个流放犯人的地方。但并没有考古证据表明波特兰岛曾经拥有这样的历史。<ref name="isleofthedead">{{cite web | year = 1999 | language = en | url = http://www.britishdowsers.org/EEG_site/archive/articles/aua2001_issue24/isleofdead_JHarvey_m.htm | title = The Isle of the Dead | publisher = British Society of Dowsers | accessdate = 2007-07-30 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20070930021015/http://www.britishdowsers.org/EEG_site/archive/articles/aua2001_issue24/isleofdead_JHarvey_m.htm | archivedate = 2007年9月30日 | df =  }}</ref>

[[托马斯·哈代|托马斯·哈代]]在他的小说中称呼波特兰岛为投石者岛（Isle of Slingers）。该岛是其小说《意中人》（{{lang|en|''The Well-Beloved''}}）的主要场景，在小说《号兵长》（''The Trumpet-Major''）中也有特写。<ref name="slingers">{{cite web | year = 2007 | language = en | url = http://www.lymeregis.com/hardy_country/ | title = Thomas Hardy County and the Hardy Trail | publisher = Lyme Regis Tourist Information | accessdate = 2007-07-26 | archive-date = 2021-03-23 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210323220816/https://www.lymeregis.com/hardy_country/ | dead-url = no }}</ref> 波特兰博物馆的建设灵感就来源于《意中人》中女主角的房子。在投石者岛上，居民为了保卫家园，熟练地掌握了投石技巧。书中的水井街（Street of Wells）的原型为福顿斯维尔，比尔（The Beal）原型为波特兰半岛。哈代将波特兰岛比喻为北方的直布罗陀，因为这里的地形地貌、与外界的隔绝、较为温和的气候以及昂德希尔的蜿蜒街道都与[[直布罗陀|直布罗陀]]相似。<ref name="wellbeloved">{{cite web | authorlink = [[Thomas_Hardy|Thomas Hardy]] | year = 2007 | language = en | url = http://www.fullbooks.com/The-Well-Beloved1.html | title = The Well-Beloved by Thomas Hardy | publisher = Full Books | accessdate = 2007-07-26 | archive-date = 2011-06-07 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110607172224/http://www.fullbooks.com/The-Well-Beloved1.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>

=== 2012年夏季奥林匹克运动会 ===
[[File:Uk_dor_sailingacademy.JPG|thumb]]
2005年，韦茅斯-波特兰国立帆船运动中心被挑选为2012年伦敦奥运会帆船赛事的举办地，主要原因是该中心是最近建造的，不需要进行太大翻修。<ref name="2012chosen">{{cite web | year = 2005 | language = en | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/england/dorset/4653721.stm | title = Sailing town's joy at Olympic win | publisher = British Broadcasting Corporation | accessdate = 2008-01-07}}</ref> 然而，英格兰西南经济发展署（South West of England Regional Development Agency）却打算重修鱼鹰港，计划包括建设一个600泊位的船坞和扩建更多的奥运赛场设施，<ref name="portlandmarina">{{cite web | year = 2007 | language = en | url = http://www.portlandmarina.co.uk | title = Dean and Reddyhoff Marina | publisher = Dean and Reddyhoff Limited | accessdate = 2007-03-26 | archive-date = 2007-09-28 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20070928223403/http://www.portlandmarina.co.uk/ | dead-url = no }}</ref> 工程于2007年10月开始进行。<ref name="wpnsaextension">{{cite web | year = 2007 | language = en | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/england/dorset/6246176.stm | title = New Olympic marina plan approved | publisher = The [[British_Broadcasting_Corporation|British Broadcasting Corporation]] | accessdate = 2007-06-27 | archive-date = 2007-08-19 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20070819124217/http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/england/dorset/6246176.stm | dead-url = no }}</ref>

韦茅斯-波特兰国立帆船运动中心在2008年年底完成了奥运赛场设施的升级工作，韦茅斯-波特兰也成为英国第一个完工的奥运比赛场馆。升级的设施包括了一个新建250米长的[[船台|船台]]和一个新的赛艇停泊处。在工程完工后，伦敦奥组委主席[[塞巴斯蒂安·科|塞巴斯蒂安·科]]以及[[2008年夏季奥林匹克运动会|北京奥运会]]金牌得主[[保罗·古迪森|保罗·古迪森]]都对韦茅斯-波特兰的新场地感到骄傲和期待。<ref>{{cite web | year = 2008 | language = en | url = http://www.sailing.org/27560.php | title = Weymouth and Portland First London 2012 Venue To Complete Construction | publisher = ISAF | accessdate = 2009-09-15 | archive-date = 2016-03-05 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160305072413/http://www.sailing.org/27560.php | dead-url = no }}</ref>2009年6月11日，[[伊丽莎白二世|伊丽莎白二世]]和[[菲利普亲王_(爱丁堡公爵)|爱丁堡公爵]]参观了波特兰的帆船运动中心。<ref name="queen">{{cite web | year = 2009 | language = en | url = http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NyBEyROnlCg&feature=channel_page | title = HM The Queen's Visit to Portland: The 2012 Olympics Sailing venue, Portland, Dorset. | publisher = Youtube | accessdate = 2009-06-11 | archive-date = 2016-09-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160911031846/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NyBEyROnlCg&feature=channel_page | dead-url = no }}</ref>

2009年8月13日，国际奥委会在[[柏林|柏林]]宣布，在伦敦奥运会上，一共将有10项有关帆船的正式比赛项目，与北京奥运会相比，减少了[[托纳多级多体船|托纳多级多体船]]赛。<ref>{{cite web | year = 2009 | language = en | url = http://www.sailing.org/29214.php | title = IOC Confirms 10 Sailing Events For London 2012 Olympic Games | publisher = ISAF | accessdate = 2009-09-14 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20090816093031/http://www.sailing.org/29214.php | archive-date = 2009-08-16 | dead-url = yes }}</ref> 另外，为了更好地推广伦敦奥运会的帆船赛事，举办方为观众准备了多种观看赛事的方式，包括免费的电视[[转播|转播]]，在周围的悬崖设立看台以及专门的收费观看船等。<ref name="2012london">{{cite web | year = 2009 | language = en | url = http://venues.london-2012.co.uk/Weymouth-and-Portland/ | title = Weymouth and Portland | publisher = The official site of the London 2012 Olympic Games | accessdate = 2009-08-16 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20080818031655/http://venues.london-2012.co.uk/Weymouth-and-Portland/ | archivedate = 2008-08-18 }}</ref> 赛事结束后，所有的设施将被留下，国立帆船运动中心将用这些设施来培养运动员，以及给当地居民娱乐。<ref name="2012london" />

